## Interactions

| Flag Combo | Behavior |
|---|---|
| `--offline` | Use cached version + cached patches only |
| `--offline --check` | Show cached version info (no network) |
| `--offline --force` | Force re-apply cached patches |
| `--offline 0.15.0` | Try to use cached patches for that specific version |
| `--offline --method npm` | Error: offline only for curl |
| (no flag, network fails) | Auto-fallback: log warning, try offline path |
| (no flag, network works) | Normal upgrade (unchanged) |

## Error Messages

| Scenario | Message |
|---|---|
| `--offline`, no cached version | `No cached version available. Run any command to trigger a background version check, then retry.` |
| `--offline`, no cached patches | `No cached patches available for upgrade to X.Y.Z. Run 'sentry cli upgrade' with network access first.` |
| Auto-fallback, no cached version | (re-throw original network error â€” no offline fallback possible) |
| Auto-fallback, no cached patches | Same as above â€” fall through to original error |
| `--offline` with brew/npm | `Offline upgrade is only supported for curl-installed binaries.` |

